	 <scopecontent encodinganalog="MARC 520"> 
		<head id="a3">COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head> 
		<p>Correspondence, reprints, photograph album from Brown University,
		  Class of 1859 and diplomas. The correspondence concerning experiments,
		  inventions, engineering and scientific problems, scientific machinery and
		  instruments includes letters from Charles Kendall Adams, Edward Atkinson,
		  Alexander Graham Bell, Alonzo Cornell, George William Curtis, Chauncey Depew,
		  Thomas A. Edison, John Ericsson, Daniel Coit Gilman, Abram Hewitt, Edwin J.
		  Houston, B.F. Isherwood, Lord Kelvin, Samuel P. Langley, Seth Low, Cyrus
		  McCormick, Charles Porter and Nikola Tesla.</p> 
	 </scopecontent> 
